This directory contains configuration and template files to 
build jsf, Satellites, etc.

This package requires ROOT.

To complete installation ,
 (1) Set following environment parameters
     ROOTSYS   : Top directory of ROOT
     LCBASEDIR : Top directory of this package
     PATH      : Command pass, include $ROOTSYS/bin and
                 $LCBASEDIR/bin. 
     LD_LIBRARY_PATH : Library path for dynamic loading
     IMAKEINCLUDE    : Include path for xmkmf
		       should include $LCBASEDIR/include

     Example will be found in conf/setup.bash

  (2) Do
     $ make

     This will create file, LCBASEConfig.h, in the include directory.

That's it
